#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/properties/path_animation.rst:5
msgid "Path Animation"
msgstr "路径动画"

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/properties/path_animation.rst:7
msgid ""
"The *Path Animation* settings can be used to determine how child objects "
"move along a certain path."
msgstr "*路径动画* 设置可用于确定子对象如何沿着特定路径移动。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/properties/path_animation.rst:11
msgid ""
"This feature is deprecated, but still available. A more future-proof method "
"is the :doc:`/animation/constraints/relationship/follow_path`."
msgstr ""
"这个特性是不推荐的，但它仍然可用。一个更适合使用的方法是 :doc:`/animation/"
"constraints/relationship/follow_path` 。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/properties/path_animation.rst:17
msgid "Path Animation panel."
msgstr "路径动画面板。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/properties/path_animation.rst:20
msgid "Frames"
msgstr "帧"

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/properties/path_animation.rst:20
msgid ""
"The number of frames that are needed to traverse the path, defining the "
"maximum value for the *Evaluation Time* setting."
msgstr "遍历路径所需的帧数，定义 *估算时刻* 设置的最大值。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/properties/path_animation.rst:25
msgid "Evaluation Time"
msgstr "估算时刻"

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/properties/path_animation.rst:23
msgid ""
"Parametric position along the length of the curve that object following it "
"should be at (the position is evaluated by dividing by the *Path Length* "
"value). By default, it is linked to the global frame number, but could be "
"keyframed to give more control over the path animation."
msgstr ""
"物体沿曲线长度跟随所在的参数化位置(通过与 *路径长度* 值相除得出估算值)。默认"
"情况下，它链接到全局帧号，但是可以通过设置关键帧对路径动画进行更多的控制。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/properties/path_animation.rst:28
msgid "Follow"
msgstr "跟随"

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/properties/path_animation.rst:28
msgid "Make the curve path children rotate along the curvature of the path."
msgstr "使曲线路径的子物体沿路径的曲率旋转。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/properties/path_animation.rst:32
msgid ""
"Deprecated, but still available use. A more future-proof method is the :doc:"
"`/animation/constraints/relationship/follow_path`."
msgstr ""
"不赞成，但仍然可用。一个更适合使用的方法是 :doc:`/animation/constraints/"
"relationship/follow_path` 。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/properties/path_animation.rst:37
msgid "Example"
msgstr "示例"

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/properties/path_animation.rst:39
msgid "This example shows you how setup a *Path Animation*."
msgstr "这个例子向您展示了如何设置一个 *路径动画* 。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/properties/path_animation.rst:41
msgid ""
"Add an object you want to animate and a path along which this object will "
"move. In this example it's the *Monkey* and the *Bézier Circle*."
msgstr ""
"添加一个要动画化的对象和该对象将沿其移动的路径。在这个例子中，它是 *猴头* 和 "
"*贝塞尔圆* 。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/properties/path_animation.rst:43
msgid ""
"To parent the monkey to the Bézier circle, first select the monkey then the "
"curve (so that the curve is the active object), press :kbd:`Ctrl-P` and "
"select *Follow Path*. It will automatically animate *Evaluation Time* and "
"activate *Follow* option in the *Path Animation* panel."
msgstr ""
"将该猴头的父级设置为贝塞尔圆，首先选择该猴头，然后选择曲线(以使该曲线是活动物"
"体)，按 :kbd:`Ctrl-P` ，然后选择 *跟随路径* 。它将自动地动画化 *估算时刻* ，"
"并激活 *路径动画* 面板中的 *跟随* 选项。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/properties/path_animation.rst:47
msgid ""
"Select the monkey and :doc:`Clear Origin </scene_layout/object/editing/"
"transform/clear_apply>` to reset its offset."
msgstr ""
"选择猴头并 :doc:`重置原点 </scene_layout/object/editing/transform/"
"clear_apply>` 来重置它的偏移量。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/properties/path_animation.rst:48
msgid ""
"You can change the orientation of the monkey by changing the :doc:`Tracking "
"Axis </scene_layout/object/properties/relations/extras>`."
msgstr ""
"你可以通过改变 :doc:`跟踪坐标轴 </scene_layout/object/properties/relations/"
"extras>` 来改变猴头的方向。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/properties/path_animation.rst:55
msgid "Monkey parented to the Bézier Circle."
msgstr "猴头以贝塞尔圆为父级。"

#: ../../manual/modeling/curves/properties/path_animation.rst:59
msgid "The final result."
msgstr "最终结果。"
